{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Carl B portfolio","author":"Carl Barrdahl"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"7a6a8cb2-1970-5af1-acf2-f3647c5cffd9","excerpt":"Pakt is a platform where users can create and share contracts. Documents are uniquely identified with a hash of its content to ensure everyone signs the sameâ€¦","html":"<p>Pakt is a platform where users can create and share contracts. Documents are uniquely identified with a hash of its content to ensure everyone signs the same copy and no tampering is done. Signing and verification of users identity is done with BankID which is the leading electronic identification app in Sweden.</p>\n<p>Other services can easily be integrated by specifying webhooks that gets triggered when changes occur in the system.</p>\n<p>Future improvements could include adding Swish (similar to BankID but for sms payments) to add costs to creating documents or signatures. Users could also be notified by sms when contracts are assigned or new signatures created to connected contract.</p>\n<p>Some documents might be sensitive to store on central servers. In that case something like <a href=\"https://ipfs.io\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">ipfs</a> could be used to store the documents and then secure them with smart contracts on a blockchain, <a href=\"http://ethereum.org\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ethereum</a> for instance.</p>\n<h3>Screenshots</h3>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/web/static/89137aaa67e0fd76627505b30e327f6c/e1f19/create.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Contract creation\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/web/static/89137aaa67e0fd76627505b30e327f6c/fb8a0/create.png\"\n        srcset=\"/web/static/89137aaa67e0fd76627505b30e327f6c/1a291/create.png 148w,\n/web/static/89137aaa67e0fd76627505b30e327f6c/2bc4a/create.png 295w,\n/web/static/89137aaa67e0fd76627505b30e327f6c/fb8a0/create.png 590w,\n/web/static/89137aaa67e0fd76627505b30e327f6c/526de/create.png 885w,\n/web/static/89137aaa67e0fd76627505b30e327f6c/fa2eb/create.png 1180w,\n/web/static/89137aaa67e0fd76627505b30e327f6c/08f6a/create.png 1770w,\n/web/static/89137aaa67e0fd76627505b30e327f6c/e1f19/create.png 2048w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \nContracts are easily created by dragging a document to upload (or browsing) and filling out the details. Start and end date for contract validity can be set and participants can be added by entering their email.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/web/static/69657204287cbd00397a8c5481ec99bd/e1f19/view.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Contract view\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/web/static/69657204287cbd00397a8c5481ec99bd/fb8a0/view.png\"\n        srcset=\"/web/static/69657204287cbd00397a8c5481ec99bd/1a291/view.png 148w,\n/web/static/69657204287cbd00397a8c5481ec99bd/2bc4a/view.png 295w,\n/web/static/69657204287cbd00397a8c5481ec99bd/fb8a0/view.png 590w,\n/web/static/69657204287cbd00397a8c5481ec99bd/526de/view.png 885w,\n/web/static/69657204287cbd00397a8c5481ec99bd/fa2eb/view.png 1180w,\n/web/static/69657204287cbd00397a8c5481ec99bd/08f6a/view.png 1770w,\n/web/static/69657204287cbd00397a8c5481ec99bd/e1f19/view.png 2048w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \nDocuments are embedded to easily be read without need of downloading. Future improvements can include templates to dynamically generate documents based on data.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/web/static/3805ae500e29c33025a42488e1786318/e1f19/sign.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Contract sign\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/web/static/3805ae500e29c33025a42488e1786318/fb8a0/sign.png\"\n        srcset=\"/web/static/3805ae500e29c33025a42488e1786318/1a291/sign.png 148w,\n/web/static/3805ae500e29c33025a42488e1786318/2bc4a/sign.png 295w,\n/web/static/3805ae500e29c33025a42488e1786318/fb8a0/sign.png 590w,\n/web/static/3805ae500e29c33025a42488e1786318/526de/sign.png 885w,\n/web/static/3805ae500e29c33025a42488e1786318/fa2eb/sign.png 1180w,\n/web/static/3805ae500e29c33025a42488e1786318/08f6a/sign.png 1770w,\n/web/static/3805ae500e29c33025a42488e1786318/e1f19/sign.png 2048w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \nSign contract by entering your SSN and open app on mobile. QR code can be added for a more secure (and convenient) signing experience.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/web/static/9c084625503f202ee80ea71e1ecb2db6/e1f19/list.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Contract list\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/web/static/9c084625503f202ee80ea71e1ecb2db6/fb8a0/list.png\"\n        srcset=\"/web/static/9c084625503f202ee80ea71e1ecb2db6/1a291/list.png 148w,\n/web/static/9c084625503f202ee80ea71e1ecb2db6/2bc4a/list.png 295w,\n/web/static/9c084625503f202ee80ea71e1ecb2db6/fb8a0/list.png 590w,\n/web/static/9c084625503f202ee80ea71e1ecb2db6/526de/list.png 885w,\n/web/static/9c084625503f202ee80ea71e1ecb2db6/fa2eb/list.png 1180w,\n/web/static/9c084625503f202ee80ea71e1ecb2db6/08f6a/list.png 1770w,\n/web/static/9c084625503f202ee80ea71e1ecb2db6/e1f19/list.png 2048w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \nAll users uploaded and signed contracts are listed.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/web/static/726e4d2432058f29cc3407d7c7d98c32/e1f19/webhooks.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Contract webhooks\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/web/static/726e4d2432058f29cc3407d7c7d98c32/fb8a0/webhooks.png\"\n        srcset=\"/web/static/726e4d2432058f29cc3407d7c7d98c32/1a291/webhooks.png 148w,\n/web/static/726e4d2432058f29cc3407d7c7d98c32/2bc4a/webhooks.png 295w,\n/web/static/726e4d2432058f29cc3407d7c7d98c32/fb8a0/webhooks.png 590w,\n/web/static/726e4d2432058f29cc3407d7c7d98c32/526de/webhooks.png 885w,\n/web/static/726e4d2432058f29cc3407d7c7d98c32/fa2eb/webhooks.png 1180w,\n/web/static/726e4d2432058f29cc3407d7c7d98c32/08f6a/webhooks.png 1770w,\n/web/static/726e4d2432058f29cc3407d7c7d98c32/e1f19/webhooks.png 2048w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>Contract in screenshots from <a href=\"https://plainfreelancecontract.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://plainfreelancecontract.com/</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Pakt","date":"January 02, 